name: Egg
description: Simple boiled eggs enhanced with a home-made spice paste and a crackling tempering. This egg masala can be a great option for dinner parties or even a casual lunch. This is a quick and super easy egg recipe. Just pair with chapati or paratha and devour a delicious meal.

name: Chicken
description: For a juicier Masala Chicken, marinate the chicken for a good 30 minutes to one hour in 1 tsp turmeric powder, 2 tbsp mustrad oil, salt and 2 tsp curd and garlic paste. Fresh tomatoes always works better than tomato puree.
